  "3308330": {
    "name": "Hardcore Circus",
    "steam_appid": 3308330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hardcore Circus</strong> 是一款受精准平台游戏和“掘地求升（Foddian）”类经典游戏启发的受苦型平台跳跃游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专为那些热爱掌控移动的满足感，以及享受在同一路段重复数百次痛苦的玩家设计。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/466f019b7fbb65a8543fc2474be66157.poster.avif?t=1765976708\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/466f019b7fbb65a8543fc2474be66157.webm?t=1765976708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/466f019b7fbb65a8543fc2474be66157.mp4?t=1765976708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>核心特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>基于动量的操控</strong>：没有武器，只有物理引擎。如果你死了，那全怪你自己。<br></li><li><strong>和平的暴力</strong>：仅利用你的移动和环境来击败邪恶的 Boss。<br></li><li><strong>动态损伤</strong>：失去四肢也能继续游戏。即使只剩躯干，你也能一路滚向胜利。<br></li><li><strong>高技术上限</strong>：专为速通玩家（Speedrunner）和完美主义者设计。<br></li><li><strong>社交功能</strong>：游戏内置多个排行榜和成就。<br></li><li><strong>瞬间重生</strong>：快速失败，立即重试。</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/b2ab1d422ad405b7a95038401e6918d2.poster.avif?t=1765976708\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/b2ab1d422ad405b7a95038401e6918d2.webm?t=1765976708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/b2ab1d422ad405b7a95038401e6918d2.mp4?t=1765976708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>认识迪克（DIK）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他不是士兵。他不是巫师。他是一个有着啤酒肚、穿着紧身衣的坚定杂技演员。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当恶魔将他的兄弟亚历克斯拖入地狱时，迪克也紧随其后跳了进去。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进入心流状态</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不仅仅是乱按按钮——你需要计算抛物线。这是一场高风险的攀爬，你需要积蓄动量，并在完美的时机起跳。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/ae8964dceb74f3775fc7039d6e975dab.poster.avif?t=1765976708\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/ae8964dceb74f3775fc7039d6e975dab.webm?t=1765976708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/ae8964dceb74f3775fc7039d6e975dab.mp4?t=1765976708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>致命的 BOSS 战</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你没有武器。Boss 战是一场激烈的生存之舞，移动是你唯一的攻击手段。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>模式识别</strong>：记住攻击模式。<br></li><li><strong>环境武器</strong>：通过触发落石、引诱敌人进入陷阱或激活激光破坏护盾来智取怪物。</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/30563bae3b7b380cb04aa7068f5eb438.poster.avif?t=1765976708\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/30563bae3b7b380cb04aa7068f5eb438.webm?t=1765976708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/30563bae3b7b380cb04aa7068f5eb438.mp4?t=1765976708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>腿是可选的</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失去了双腿？你会变成一个滚动的躯干。这看起来很滑稽，但只要你有技术，依然可以通关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失去了双手？游戏结束。你需要它们来攀爬。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一机制将濒临失败的瞬间变成了绝望而搞笑的求生挣扎。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扭曲的世界巡演</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恶魔对室内设计有着奇怪的品味，你将在以下场景中跑酷：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >马戏团、城堡、地狱、海洋、大草原和高塔</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/6fa6c1ba7d828bf409b29a3476c0f436.poster.avif?t=1765976708\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/6fa6c1ba7d828bf409b29a3476c0f436.webm?t=1765976708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308330/extras/6fa6c1ba7d828bf409b29a3476c0f436.mp4?t=1765976708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 波兰语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 繁体中文, 简体中文, 日语, 韩语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 瑞典语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 丹麦语, 荷兰语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
